Quote: shottie <i>v.</i> [1980s+] (N.Z. drugs)to inhale a puff of marijuana cigarette through a large funnel and then drop from a standing position to a crouch when the lungs are filled to capacity, to force more smoke into the lungs [abbr. SE. <i>shotgun</i>]
